{"tid":496150,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[薄酬] 請巴打幫手做份 C++ STL 功課","createTime":"2017-12-11T11:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T14:40:53.000Z","uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c21a3a70cb9812099bbf1d1fccb50e9456559047","tid":496150,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n程度係 2 字頭入門水平，內容：<br />\n1. 整個 Vector Class 儲 n 條 integer Sequence (User input 兩樣野：Sequence 長度 + Sequence 內容)<br />\n2. 由細至大，橫向咁 Sort 好每條 Seq 再儲入 Class<br />\n3. 根據某啲定義將 n 條 Sequence 竪直咁 Sort 好，我估意思應該係 Sort 係 Vector 既次序<br />\n4. Output 哂 sort 完既所有 Sequence"},{"pid":"2ef9c57d5ab45ae88672b65d0b4bcae7825639d6","tid":496150,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:53:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/poorcsjj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fpoorcsjj&d=uA28R6JCBz47jVp7SP3IoW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a8c881f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/poorcsjj</a><br />\n<br />\n請巴打聯絡我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我再比問題你睇，睇完先決定價錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4ee0ae3a99e0a6c384b177b5d1435cc56fafee","tid":496150,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"我估熟手巴打應該 1 小時搞掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f86966d32f5ff951f0757a3e08b890e4666703e","tid":496150,"uid":14170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:57:48.000Z","msg":"其實係一份功課入面既一條 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就快考另一科 final 所以無時間磨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc0a315a0746b5ebea3